---
---
<section class="page-container section-spacer">
  <div class="glow-line"></div>
  <p class="eyebrow fade-in">paths</p>
  <h2 class="fade-in-up delay-1" style="max-width: 500px; margin-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);">Same core. Different friction.</h2>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);">
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-2">
      <div class="card-cyber">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.6875rem;">patreon</p>
        <p style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; color: var(--color-cyan);">$5-15/mo</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Polished installers, auto-updates, priority support. Best for most people.</p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">One-click Docker installer</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Pre-built PWA</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Auto-update notifications</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Priority support</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Early beta access</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://patreon.com/kxnotes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-cyber-filled" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Get elly</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-3">
      <div class="card-cyber">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.6875rem;">self-host</p>
        <p style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; color: var(--color-ink);">Free</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Same core, you build the PWA. For tinkerers and privacy maxis.</p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">docker compose up</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Full source access</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Modify freely</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Runs on Raspberry Pi</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">No account needed</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://github.com/Kxetch/kx-notes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-cyber" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">View on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-4">
      <div class="card-cyber">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.6875rem;">contribute</p>
        <p style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; color: var(--color-ink);">Open source</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Local dev with hot reload. Pull requests welcome.</p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">TypeScript + Python</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">128 tests passing</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">MCP server included</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Design principles in AGENTS.md</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-family: var(--font-mono);">Code of Conduct enforced</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://github.com/Kxetch/kx-notes/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-cyber" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Read CONTRIBUTING.md</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
